window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Everything I thought I knew about my world has been shattered.</p> <p>The only constant are the four Monsters keeping me and my people safe.</p> <p>My only comfort in my grief is Bastian, the last of my team.</p> <p>And our only certainty is that we need to find the pieces of the relic and put it back together.</p> <p>As Shem and I work together, I find myself dropping my guard around him. He's lethal, single-minded, and unyielding, and he's the only one that can help me put my world back to rights.</p> <p>But the road won't be easy, and trust comes at a cost. I just hope that when the time arrives, we'll be willing to pay the price.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
